---

<Layout title="Services">
  <Container>
    <main
      class="grid lg:grid-cols-7 place-items-center relative justify-items-center"
    >
      <div class="md:max-w-max lg:col-span-3 place-self-start mt-10">
        <hgroup>
          <h3 class="text-sm [text-wrap:balance] text-start">What We Offer</h3>
          <h1 class="font-bold lg:tracking-tight lg:text-start text-5xl">
            Call us a production studio with a creative drive.
          </h1>
          <h2 class="text-xl mt-4 lg:[text-wrap:balance] text-start">
            Our work focused on efficiency, consistency and quality in both
            deliverables and service. We can help your business achieve its
            goals with a no BS approach to teamwork on making those goals a
            reality.
          </h2>
        </hgroup>
      </div>

      <div class="py-3 lg:col-span-3 lg:-mr-44 max-w-[600px] mx-1">
        <Image
          src={servicesImage}
          alt="Services "
          sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 50vw"
          widths={[240, 540, 720]}
          loading="eager"
          fetchpriority="high"
        />
      </div>
    </main>
  </Container>

  <ServicesBlock sectionInfo={webDev} imageLoad="eager" />
  <Container class="text-xl mt-10">
    <div class="">
      Shugert is a collaborative web design and development studio designed to
      take the stress out of Shopify. With over a decade of experience as
      ecommerce experts, we enhance, optimize, and custom-build sites on <a
        href="https://shugert.com.mx/shopify-experts"
        >Shopify and Shopify Plus</a
      >, helping time-pressed businesses and growing brands make the most of
      their online store. We’ll focus on ensuring your site captures and
      converts (cha-ching)—so you can focus on your business.
      <br /><br />
      Because you’re not a Shopify expert—but your customers don’t need to know that.
      <a href="#">Learn More</a>
      <br /><br />
    </div>
    And of course, we are:
    <a
      class="max-w-[200px] inline-block"
      href="https://experts.shopify.com/shugert-marketing"
    >
      <Image
        src={shopifyExpert}
        alt="Shopify Expert"
        widths={[240, 540, 720]}
        loading="eager"
        fetchpriority="high"
      />
    </a>
  </Container>
  <Separator />

  <ServicesBlock sectionInfo={machineLearn} imageLoad="lazy" />
  <Separator />
  <ServicesBlock sectionInfo={customContent} imageLoad="lazy" />
  <Separator />
  <ServicesBlock sectionInfo={socialNet} imageLoad="lazy" />
  <Separator />
  <ServicesBlock sectionInfo={customPub} imageLoad="lazy" />
</Layout>
